# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project: datasets, model weights, and run outputs
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTE: these directory rules are anchored with a leading "/" so they only match
# at the repo root and never swallow same-named source packages such as
# ``src/reid/data/``.
